-- FrieslandCampina Gets Approval to Buy Imlek, Mlekara Subotica
-- B y   M i s h a   S a v i c
-- 2012-04-26T07:22:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-26/frieslandcampina-gets-approval-to-buy-imlek-mlekara-subotica.html
Serbia’s competition regulator
approved the purchase of two dairies, including the country’s
biggest  Imlek AD (IMLK) , by Royal FrieslandCampina NV.  The debt-financed takeover from Salford Capital Partners
Inc.’s Danube Foods Group BV, was announced on Feb. 2 and
Serbia’s  Commission for Protection of Competition  said on its
website it approves the acquisition of “at least” 81.68
percent of Imlek and 81.76 percent of Mlekara Subotica.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Misha Savic in Belgrade at 
 msavic2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  